<h1>Calculated Results</h1>
<h2>Total Carbon Footprint:
  <%= @survey.calculate_footprint%> pounds of CO2</h2>

<h3>Carbon Footprint by category</h2>
<ul>
<li>Food</li>
<p><%= @survey.calculate_footprint_by_category('food')%> pounds of CO2</p>
<li>Transportation</li>
<p><%= @survey.calculate_footprint_by_category('transportation')%> pounds of CO2</p>
<li>Lifestyle</li>
<p><%= @survey.calculate_footprint_by_category('lifestyle')%> pounds of CO2</p>


<li>Worst Item calculated</li>
<p>The survey question was: <%=@survey.worst_question_carbon_offender.content %></p>
<p>Your answer: <%= @survey.worst_impact_item_carbon_offender.name %></p>
<p>Quantity: <%= @survey.worst_response_carbon_offender.quantity %>
<p>Carbon amount: <%= @survey.worst_impact_item_carbon_offender.carbon %></p>
<p>Total carbon footprint for this response: <%= (@survey.worst_impact_item_carbon_offender.carbon * @survey.worst_impact_item_carbon_offender.carbon).round(2) %> pounds of CO2 </p>
<p>Tips for reducing: <%= @survey.worst_impact_item_carbon_offender.suggestion %></p>
</ul>

<%=link_to "Calculate Your Carbon Footprint", surveys_path, method: :post %>
